	<h2 class="normal mt5 tc">The Vineyard Family</h2>
   		
	<div class="w-100 center cf mb4"> 
		<!-- COL 1 -->
		<div class="fl w-100 w-50-ns ph4">
			<h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Erin Begerow</h3>
			<p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Office manager. She is a native Californian, and a graduate of Pomona College. Erin takes care of all office work, and started working for the Dunn&#8217;s in October of 1994. She and her husband live just down the road from the winery. They have two children, both of whom are in college now. She also coaches the Waves Aquatics swim team.</p>
			<h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Raul Martinez</h3>
			<p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Vineyard manager Raul Martinez was the first employee. He came on in 1987 to help Randy in the vineyards and he is still running the vineyard today.</p>
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Adan Salgado</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Adan joined the crew in 2001 and has been an invaluable contributer ever since. He's the one to thank for the wax on the Howell Mountain bottles. It's not an easy job but Adan cranks them out at 100 cases per day!</p>
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Marcos Olivera</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Brought on in 2005. Formerly he worked for the tunnel guys that dug our cave. Marcos is the back bone of the vineyard crew. Today he supervises the guys as Raul has many other duties to attend to.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="fl w-100 w-50-ns ph4">
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Rosalio Olivera</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Rosalio came onboard in 2005 to help in the vineyard and has been a valuable member of the team ever since.</p>
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Adriaan Foote</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Joining in 2014, Adriaan came over to help Mike in the cellar. He is a trained winemaker from South Africa and makes a small amount of Napa Valley and South African Chardonnay (<%= link_to "Hand of Fate", "http://www.handoffatewines.com", :class => "dim link dunn-link", :target => "_blank" %>) in conjunction with his Cabernet duties at the winery.</p>
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Ben Hiza</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Ben arrived in time to help with the 2013 bottling and hasn't left yet. While he's in charge of distribution and tours, he's already ready to help with whatever needs doing.</p>
        <h3 class="normal mt4 mb0">Fernando Olivera</h3>
        <p class="lh-copy measure mt2">Starting in 2015, he is the third member of this Olivera clan here in the vineyard. Fernando always has a smile on his face and laughs at all of Mike's jokes so he certainly has a successful future here in the vineyard.</p>
		</div>
